page.title: 10Daily Life.
page.content: 1. Do you work? yes. 2. What is your job? a barmaid. 3. Are you self employed? no. 4. Do you enjoy your job? yes. 5. Do you do your job because you. need the money, because you enjoy it. or because you have to? have to. 6. Do you work shifts? no. 7. What hours do you work? variable. 8. What are you: well or badly paid? badly. 9. What do you do for leisure? walking and reading. 10. Do you eat at the same time as the rest of your family? seldom. 11. What time do you finish work? 12:00 midnight. 12. What time do you normally go to bed? 1:00 to 2:00am.
